{"id":646719,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/06/【立此存照】武汉网友拍摄出租车罢工运动遭喝/","date":"2020-06-09T17:08:33Z","modified":"2020-06-09T17:23:34Z","title":"【立此存照】武汉网友拍摄出租车罢工运动遭“喝茶”","content":"<p>近日，一名武汉网友因拍摄了当地一段“出租车罢工”视频上传至微信群，遭到“江岸分局花桥派出所”几名便衣的电话传唤（以诱骗方式）与问话，并登记了“个人详细资料”，告诫非常时期勿“乱拍乱发”视频。警方在谈话中透露该视频被其他网友传送至海外平台，这也显示出武汉警方对当地信息的“外传”有着密切的监控。</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"武汉网友拍摄当地“疫情时期”出租车罢工运动遭“喝茶”\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0sxgwWrfqR4?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/EaFACS_U0AIoiE_.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646721\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/EaFACS_U0AIoiE_.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"560\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/EaFACS_U0AIoiE_.jpeg 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/EaFACS_U0AIoiE_-241x300.jpeg 241w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1002,"categories":[18271,38912,39484,38927],"tags":[8714,9249,39764,13381,39648,8888,10778,40805]}